149
00:09:12,860 --> 00:09:14,820
I've been a fool all along!

150
00:09:15,060 --> 00:09:15,580
No...

151
00:09:15,580 --> 00:09:17,150
He Xiao, you're unbelievable!

152
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:17,700
Wei...

153
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:18,820
You wretch.

154
