157
00:09:25,550 --> 00:09:26,150
Wei,

158
00:09:26,150 --> 00:09:26,860
let me explain.

159
00:10:14,980 --> 00:10:16,910
(If I can't reach you even once,)

160
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:18,700
(your boyfriend will receive
more videos,)

161
00:10:18,700 --> 00:10:20,580
(including your friends and colleagues.)

162
00:10:20,580 --> 00:10:21,740
