164
00:10:24,220 --> 00:10:24,820
(You wretch.)

165
00:10:24,900 --> 00:10:26,950
(If you try to contact me again,
I'll make you pay!)

166
00:10:27,270 --> 00:10:28,270
(Screw you!)

167
00:10:28,510 --> 00:10:29,310
(You wretch.)

168
00:10:29,310 --> 00:10:30,270
(Screw you!)

169
00:11:12,510 --> 00:11:14,060
No!

170
00:11:16,340 --> 00:11:18,100
Xiao!

171
00:12:37,860 --> 00:12:38,820
Since you knew

172
00:12:39,270 --> 00:12:40,820
Liu Ang was spreading those videos

173
00:12:41,460 --> 00:12:43,150
and you had the evidence,

174
00:12:43,450 --> 00:12:44,690
