175
00:12:45,790 --> 00:12:46,340
The police?

176
00:12:47,700 --> 00:12:48,580
What could they do?

177
00:12:49,980 --> 00:12:50,580
Also,

178
00:12:51,030 --> 00:12:54,150
the security footage showed
He Xiao jumping on her own.

179
00:12:54,940 --> 00:12:56,190
Even if Liu Ang is sentenced,

180
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:57,460
how many years will he get?

181
00:12:57,740 --> 00:12:58,630
So instead,

182
00:13:00,150 --> 00:13:01,460
you chose revenge.

183
00:13:02,700 --> 00:13:04,820
You ruined yourself to take him down?
Was it worth it?

184
00:13:15,700 --> 00:13:16,820
After He Xiao jumped,

185
00:13:18,460 --> 00:13:19,580
she lay in a pool of blood.

186
00:13:21,740 --> 00:13:22,940
Her ribs punctured

187
