196
00:13:50,060 --> 00:13:50,910
struggling,

197
00:13:51,670 --> 00:13:53,270
and unable to make a sound.

198
00:13:54,190 --> 00:13:55,390
So hilarious.

199
00:13:56,340 --> 00:13:57,860
Absolutely hilarious!

200
00:14:03,390 --> 00:14:04,430
So you admit

201
00:14:04,910 --> 00:14:06,060
