202
00:14:06,580 --> 00:14:07,790
He loved being a player, right?

203
00:14:08,340 --> 00:14:08,980
All right, then.

204
00:14:09,790 --> 00:14:12,860
So I made sure he died
playing in his favorite place.

205
00:14:13,550 --> 00:14:14,980
So long as he is rotting in hell,

206
