212
00:14:29,910 --> 00:14:31,980
when she needed him most?

213
00:14:34,270 --> 00:14:35,310
Living

214
00:14:35,310 --> 00:14:36,790
in darkness forever

215
00:14:37,550 --> 00:14:38,580
isn't the scariest thing.

216
00:14:39,340 --> 00:14:40,310
The scariest is knowing

217
00:14:40,310 --> 00:14:41,550
what hope feels like.

218
00:14:42,790 --> 00:14:44,270
Xiao saw hope.

219
00:14:45,820 --> 00:14:47,790
And for her, that hope was Wei.

220
00:14:49,060 --> 00:14:51,030
But when she was at her weakest,

221
00:14:51,030 --> 00:14:51,670
he destroyed

222
00:14:52,270 --> 00:14:53,460
that hope.

223
00:14:53,820 --> 00:14:54,700
He destroyed it!

224
00:14:59,220 --> 00:15:01,100
But Lei Wei didn't know

225
00:15:01,100 --> 00:15:02,670
Liu Ang was blackmailing her.

226
00:15:03,430 --> 00:15:04,940
Then why did he break up with her?

227
00:15:06,340 --> 00:15:08,270
Why did he leave her
at that exact moment?

228
00:15:08,910 --> 00:15:10,670
Why couldn't he believe her,

229
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:14,390
the woman he was going to marry?

230
00:15:15,390 --> 00:15:17,190
He was the one who let go

231
00:15:17,190 --> 00:15:19,510
