too much in her life.

261
00:16:45,590 --> 00:16:47,540
I wanted to give her a good future.

262
00:16:49,780 --> 00:16:52,460
I worked so hard in the city

263
00:16:53,670 --> 00:16:55,870
for over twenty years

264
00:16:56,350 --> 00:16:58,630
and finally made something of myself.

265
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:01,830
I thought

266
00:17:01,830 --> 00:17:03,190
if I had money,

267
00:17:03,740 --> 00:17:06,110
my daughter would finally accept me,

268
00:17:06,390 --> 00:17:08,020
